69handle_dot_label(YYSTYPE *lvalp, char *tok, size_t toklen, size_t zeropos,
70 yasm_parser_nasm *parser_nasm)
71{
72 /* check for special non-local labels like ..start */

75 toklen-zeropos-(parser_nasm->tasm?2:0));
76 /* check for special non-local ..@label */
77 if (lvalp->str_val[zeropos+2] == '@')
78 return NONLOCAL_ID;
79 return SPECIAL_ID;
80 }
81 if (parser_nasm->masm && tok[zeropos] == '.') {
82 lvalp->str_val = yasm__xstrndup(tok + zeropos, toklen - zeropos);
83 return SPECIAL_ID;
84 }
85 if (parser_nasm->tasm && (!tasm_locals ||
86 (tok[zeropos] == '.' &&
87 tok[zeropos+1] != '@' && tok[zeropos+2] != '@'))) {
88 /* no locals on Tasm without the 'locals' directive */
89 /* .foo is never local either, but .@@foo may be (local structure
90 * members) */
91 lvalp->str_val = yasm__xstrndup(tok + zeropos, toklen - zeropos);
92 return SPECIAL_ID;
93 }
94 if (!parser_nasm->locallabel_base) {
95 lvalp->str_val = yasm__xstrndup(tok+zeropos, toklen-zeropos);
96 yasm_warn_set(YASM_WARN_GENERAL,
97 N_("no non-local label before `%s'"),
98 lvalp->str_val);
99 } else {
100 size_t len = toklen - zeropos + parser_nasm->locallabel_base_len;
101 lvalp->str_val = yasm_xmalloc(len + 1);
102 strcpy(lvalp->str_val, parser_nasm->locallabel_base);
103 strncat(lvalp->str_val, tok+zeropos, toklen-zeropos);
104 lvalp->str_val[len] = '\0';
105 }
106
107 return LOCAL_ID;
